<h1 id="omit-needless-words">Omit Needless Words</h1>

<p><em>The Elements of Style</em> by Strunk and White may be considered outdated
by many<sup id="fnref:1"><a href="#fn:1" class="footnote">1</a></sup>, but I do love the classic advice of â€œomit needless wordsâ€.</p>

<p>Before you send an email, go through each paragraph and remove as many
