<p>At work employers have access to all of your emails. Act accordingly.</p>

<h1 id="lock-it-down">Lock It Down</h1>

<p>Hopefully Iâ€™ve convinced you of some of emailâ€™s power. I want to leave
you with one last piece of advice: secure your damn email. Thereâ€™s a
lot of criticism towards the mandatory Multi Factor Authentication on
